data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully maintained two story home in the gated community of Harper's Preserve! This home offers four bedrooms and three and a half bathrooms, with a formal dining room, home office, and spacious living room. You will love the open kitchen complete with a large granite island and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom includes an en suite bathroom with dual vanities, a large walk-in closet, and sitting area. Upstairs you will find three more bedrooms, two bathrooms, a game room and media room! Spend the afternoon relaxing on your large covered back patio. This home is a perfect combination of beauty, comfort, and convenience located in Conroe ISD. Schedule a private tour today!
